margin-left:0in;text-align:justify'>The generated game features will be described in this section. After compiling the Game Project as it was described in Section 4, the “Web Link” button can be used to play the game online. Alternatively, if the game was compiled for Windows, Mac, or Linux, the zipped binary should be downloaded, extracted, and the binary “mygame.exe” should be ran. For binary type of games ignore any certification questions as our server is in testing mode and does not produce digitally signed games. The initial page of the game is the Main Menu as shown in Figure 14. The image is the one selected in Scenario 1 for Main Menu scene.</p>

